data.description: This home is conveniently located near 58th & Georgia/Western. This Home includes a finished basement, sunken living room, cathedral ceilings, and a covered patio. Updates include newer carpet, new flooring in the basement/stairs, a new AC unit, a class 4 roof, and much more to see in person. Schedule your appointment today!
